511
00:31:10,631 --> 00:31:12,231
Would you like to try sitting in it?

512
00:31:17,271 --> 00:31:19,771
Wow. It really suits him,
doesn't it?

513
00:31:21,181 --> 00:31:22,981
How does it feel?

514
00:31:27,051 --> 00:31:29,021
